-- Edison May Sell 55% of Buran Wind Project Unit, Italian Daily MF Reports
-- Tommaso Ebhardt
-- 2010-06-15T06:05:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-15/edison-may-sell-55-of-buran-wind-project-unit-italian-daily-mf-reports.html

          
          
             Edison SpA may form a wind power
unit called Buran Wind Project and sell 55 percent of it to
investors, Italian daily MF reported, without saying where it
got the information.  
 The Italian utility may also consider listing the unit from
2015, the Italian daily said.  
          
          


  


        